<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>YPI | In-Person Volunteer Database</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<script>
tailwind.config = {
darkMode: 'class',
theme: {
extend: {
colors: {
ypi: {
green: '#37af4b',
dark: '#1c1c1c',
card: '#252525',
hover: '#2d8c3c',
glow: '#98fb98'
}
},
fontFamily: {
sans: ['Atkinson Hyperlegible', 'sans-serif'],
mono: ['ui-monospace', 'SFMono-Regular', 'Menlo', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', 'Liberation Mono', 'Courier New', 'monospace']
}
}
}
}
</script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Atkinson+Hyperlegible:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
<script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
<style>
:root {
--bg-main: #121212;
--bg-panel: #1c1c1c;
--bg-element: #252525;
--text-main: #ffffff;
--text-muted: #9ca3af;
--border-color: #333;
--accent-green: #37af4b;
--highlight-green: #98fb98;
--danger-red: #ef4444;
}
body {
background-color: var(--bg-main);
color: #f0f0f0;
font-family: 'Atkinson Hyperlegible', sans-serif;
margin: 0;
overflow: hidden;
}
.font-fm-header { font-family: 'Atkinson Hyperlegible', sans-serif; }
.no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.no-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #1a1a1a; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #333; border-radius: 3px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--accent-green); }

.fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out; }
@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

.tab-content { display: none; }
.tab-content.active { display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: calc(100vh - 64px); }

/* Header */
header { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }

/* Layout */
.dashboard-layout { display: flex; flex: 1; overflow: hidden; }
.sidebar { width: 280px; background: var(--bg-panel); border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow-y: auto; flex-shrink: 0; }
.main-panel { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; background: var(--bg-main); }

/* Sidebar Sections */
.sidebar-section { padding: 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.sidebar-title { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--highlight-green); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
.filter-group { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.filter-label { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; display: block; }
.filter-select, .filter-input {
width: 100%; background: var(--bg-element); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); color: var(--text-main);
padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.85rem; outline: none; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.filter-select:focus, .filter-input:focus { border-color: var(--highlight-green); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.1); }

/* Query Builder */
.query-header { background: var(--bg-panel); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.query-tabs { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; height: 100%; align-items: flex-end; }
.query-tab {
padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: var(--text-muted); transition: all 0.2s; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
}
.query-tab.active { border-color: var(--accent-green); color: var(--highlight-green); }
.query-tab:hover { color: var(--text-main); }

.match-strategy { display: flex; background: var(--bg-element); border-radius: 6px; padding: 2px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.strategy-btn {
padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s; background: transparent; border: none; color: var(--text-muted);
}
.strategy-btn.active { background: rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.15); color: var(--highlight-green); }

.query-area { padding: 1.5rem; overflow-y: auto; background: var(--bg-main); flex: 1; }
.query-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.logic-operator {
width: 60px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
background: var(--bg-element); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 4px;
font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; font-family: monospace; color: var(--highlight-green);
}
.logic-select {
width: 60px; height: 36px; background: var(--bg-element); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 4px;
font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; font-family: monospace; color: #a78bfa; outline: none; cursor: pointer;
}
.query-input-group {
flex: 1; display: flex; background: var(--bg-element); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.5rem; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; transition: all 0.2s;
}
.query-input-group:hover { border-color: #444; }
.query-field, .query-op, .query-val { background: transparent; border: none; outline: none; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-main); }
.query-field { flex: 0 0 25%; font-weight: 600; }
.query-op { flex: 0 0 15%; color: #60a5fa; font-weight: 500; }
.query-val { flex: 1; }

.add-condition-btn {
margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-left: 60px; width: calc(100% - 60px); padding: 0.75rem;
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px dashed var(--border-color); border-radius: 6px;
color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; transition: all 0.2s;
display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem;
}
.add-condition-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent-green); color: var(--highlight-green); background: rgba(55, 175, 75, 0.05); }

.remove-btn { width: 32px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer; border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.2s; background: transparent; border: none; }
.remove-btn:hover { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); color: var(--danger-red); }

/* Results Panel */
.results-bar {
background: var(--bg-panel); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
}
.results-stats { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
.stat-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
.stat-value { font-weight: 700; color: var(--highlight-green); font-family: monospace; }
.results-grid-container { flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--bg-main); }
.results-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(340px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }

/* Volunteer Card */
.vol-card {
background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 10px; padding: 1rem;
position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); cursor: pointer;
}
.vol-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); border-color: var(--accent-green); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
.vol-card::before {
content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 3px; height: 100%; background: var(--accent-green);
opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.vol-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

.vol-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.vol-avatar { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: #2a2d35; border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; color: var(--highlight-green); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.vol-info { flex: 1; }
.vol-name { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-main); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
.vol-role { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
.vol-status { padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }
.status-active { background: rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.1); color: var(--highlight-green); border: 1px solid rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.2); }
.status-priority { background: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.1); color: #fbbf24; border: 1px solid rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.2); }
.status-dormant { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1); color: #ef4444; border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); }

.vol-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.vol-tag { background: var(--bg-element); color: var(--text-muted); padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.65rem; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }

.vol-metrics { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.metric-box { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); padding: 0.4rem; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.metric-label { font-size: 0.6rem; color: var(--text-muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
.metric-val { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; font-family: monospace; color: var(--text-main); }
.metric-high { color: var(--highlight-green); }

.vol-footer { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; padding-top: 0.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.vol-btn { flex: 1; padding: 0.4rem; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; border: none; }
.btn-primary { background: var(--accent-green); color: white; }
.btn-primary:hover { background: #2d8c3c; transform: scale(1.02); }
.btn-secondary { background: var(--bg-element); color: var(--text-muted); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
.btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--text-main); border-color: var(--text-muted); }

/* Modal */
.modal-overlay {
display: none; position: fixed; z-index: 2000; left: 0; top: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.modal-overlay.active { display: flex; }
.vol-modal-container {
background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 12px;
max-width: 900px; width: 95%; max-height: 85vh; overflow-y: auto; box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
animation: slideUp 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
@keyframes slideUp { from { transform: translateY(40px); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } }
.close-modal { position: absolute; top: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--text-muted); background: var(--bg-element); width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); transition: all 0.2s; z-index: 10; }
.close-modal:hover { color: var(--highlight-green); border-color: var(--highlight-green); }
.modal-header { padding: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); position: relative; }
.modal-body { padding: 2rem; }
.modal-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
.section-title { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--highlight-green); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.timeline-item { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 2px solid var(--border-color); position: relative; }
.timeline-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -6px; top: 0; width: 10px; height: 10px; background: var(--accent-green); border-radius: 50%; }
.timeline-date { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); min-width: 80px; }
.timeline-content { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-main); }
.timeline-type { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--highlight-green); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }

/* Attribute Library */
.library-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
.lib-card { background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.lib-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-green); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.lib-title { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
.lib-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.lib-add-btn { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--highlight-green); cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; background: rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.05); padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem; }
.lib-add-btn:hover { background: rgba(152, 251, 152, 0.15); }

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
.sidebar { width: 240px; }
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
.dashboard-layout { flex-direction: column; overflow-y: auto; height: auto; }
.sidebar { width: 100%; max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto; }
.main-panel { overflow: visible; height: auto; }
.modal-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="flex flex-col w-full bg-[#1b1b1b] border-b border-[#2a2a2a] shadow-lg sticky top-0 z-50">
<div class="flex items-center h-16 px-6 gap-6 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar">
<div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-4">
<div class="h-10 w-auto flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl tracking-tight text-white">
<i data-lucide="shield" class="w-6 h-6 mr-2 text-[#98fb98]"></i>
<span>YPI <span class="text-[#98fb98] font-light">|</span> <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-400">Field Intelligence</span></span>
</div>
</div>
<nav class="flex items-center gap-2" id="main-nav">
<!-- JS generated nav -->
</nav>
<div class="ml-auto flex items-center gap-3">
<button class="p-2 rounded-lg bg-[#2a2d35] border border-[#333] hover:border-[#98fb98] transition text-[#98fb98] relative">
<i data-lucide="bell" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
<span class="absolute top-1 right-1 w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></span>
</button>
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#2a2d35] border border-[#333] flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-white cursor-pointer">
JD
</div>
</div>
</div>
</header>

<div class="main-content w-full">
<section id="content-Volunteer-Database" class="tab-content active">
<div class="dashboard-layout">
<!-- LEFT SIDEBAR -->
<aside class="sidebar">
<div class="sidebar-section">
<div class="sidebar-title"><i data-lucide="filter" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Core Criteria</div>
<div class="filter-group">
<label class="filter-label">Volunteer Type</label>
<select class="filter-select"><option>All Types</option><option>Canvasser</option><option>Phone Banker</option><option>Event Staff</option><option>Data Entry</option></select>
</div>
<div class="filter-group">
<label class="filter-label">Experience Level</label>
<select class="filter-select"><option>Any Level</option><option>Novice</option><option>Intermediate</option><option>Veteran</option></select>
</div>
<div class="filter-group">
<label class="filter-label">Region</label>
<select class="filter-select"><option>All Regions</option><option>Montgomery County</option><option>Prince George's</option><option>Howard County</option></select>
</div>
<div class="filter-group">
<label class="filter-label">Availability</label>
<select class="filter-select"><option>Any Availability</option><option>Weekdays Only</option><option>Weekends Only</option><option>Evenings</option><option>Full Time</option></select>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sidebar-section">
<div class="sidebar-title"><i data-lucide="bookmark" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Saved Presets</div>
<div class="space-y-1">
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-[#98fb98] bg-[#98fb98]/5 border border-[#98fb98]/20 rounded hover:bg-[#98fb98]/10 transition">Active Weekend Canvassers</button>
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 rounded transition">High School Organizers</button>
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 rounded transition">Event Leadership Pool</button>
<button class="w-full text-left px-3 py-2 text-xs font-mono text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5 rounded transition">Dormant Reactivation</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sidebar-section">
<div class="sidebar-title"><i data-lucide="activity" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Pipeline Status</div>
<div class="space-y-1">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-400 px-2 py-1"><span>Active</span><span class="text-[#98fb98] font-mono">482</span></div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-400 px-2 py-1"><span>High Priority</span><span class="text-yellow-400 font-mono">15</span></div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-400 px-2 py-1"><span>Dormant</span><span class="text-red-400 font-mono">84</span></div>
</div>
</div>
</aside>

<!-- MAIN PANEL -->
<main class="main-panel">
<div class="query-header">
<div class="query-tabs">
<div class="query-tab active" id="tab-filters" onclick="switchTab('filters')"><i data-lucide="zap" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Advanced Filters <span class="bg-[#333] text-gray-300 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[10px] ml-1" id="filter-count">2</span></div>
<div class="query-tab" id="tab-library" onclick="switchTab('library')"><i data-lucide="database" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Attribute Library</div>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase">Match Strategy:</span>
<div class="match-strategy">
<button class="strategy-btn active" id="mode-strict" onclick="setMatchMode('strict')">STRICT (ALL)</button>
<button class="strategy-btn" id="mode-flex" onclick="setMatchMode('flex')">FLEX (ANY)</button>
<button class="strategy-btn" id="mode-custom" onclick="setMatchMode('custom')">CUSTOM</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="query-area" id="query-view">
<div class="space-y-3 relative">
<div class="absolute left-[22px] top-4 bottom-12 w-0.5 bg-[#333] -z-10"></div>
<div id="query-rows-container">
<!-- Rows injected here -->
</div>
<button class="add-condition-btn" onclick="addQueryRow()"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Add Advanced Filter</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="query-area hidden" id="library-view">
<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Attribute Library</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Browse available data points to filter your volunteer targeting lists.</p>
<div class="library-grid">
<div class="lib-card"><div class="lib-title"><i data-lucide="activity" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#98fb98]"></i> evL+ Score</div><div class="lib-desc">Engagement Value Level metric. Numeric range 0-1000.</div><div class="lib-add-btn"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Add to Filters</div></div>
<div class="lib-card"><div class="lib-title"><i data-lucide="graduation-cap" class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-400"></i> GPA</div><div class="lib-desc">Academic performance data. Decimal value.</div><div class="lib-add-btn"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Add to Filters</div></div>
<div class="lib-card"><div class="lib-title"><i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400"></i> Location / ZIP</div><div class="lib-desc">Geographic targeting. Text match.</div><div class="lib-add-btn"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Add to Filters</div></div>
<div class="lib-card"><div class="lib-title"><i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400"></i> Status</div><div class="lib-desc">Current volunteer status. Select: Active, Dormant, Priority.</div><div class="lib-add-btn"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Add to Filters</div></div>
<div class="lib-card"><div class="lib-title"><i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-4 h-4 text-pink-400"></i> Availability</div><div class="lib-desc">Time-based availability. Select or Range.</div><div class="lib-add-btn"><i data-lucide="plus" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Add to Filters</div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="results-bar">
<div class="results-stats">
<div class="stat-item"><i data-lucide="search" class="w-3 h-3 text-gray-400"></i> Estimated Matches: <span class="stat-value">142</span></div>
<div class="stat-item"><i data-lucide="star" class="w-3 h-3 text-yellow-400"></i> High Priority: <span class="stat-value text-yellow-400">15</span></div>
<div class="stat-item"><i data-lucide="clock" class="w-3 h-3 text-gray-400"></i> Recently Active: <span class="stat-value">42</span></div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-2">
<button class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-white px-2 py-1 transition"><i data-lucide="sort-asc" class="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1"></i> Sort</button>
<button class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 hover:text-white px-2 py-1 transition"><i data-lucide="download" class="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1"></i> Export</button>
<button class="bg-[#37af4b] hover:bg-[#2d8c3c] text-white text-xs font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded transition shadow-lg shadow-green-900/20"><i data-lucide="search" class="w-3 h-3 inline mr-1"></i> Run Query</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="results-grid-container">
<div class="results-grid" id="volunteers-grid">
<!-- Volunteer cards injected via JS -->
</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>
</section>

<!-- Volunteer Detail Modal -->
<div id="volunteerModal" class="modal-overlay">
<div class="vol-modal-container relative">
<button class="close-modal" onclick="closeVolunteerModal()"><i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5"></i></button>
<div class="modal-header">
<div class="flex items-start justify-between">
